      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable, functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scuffs, minor dings, and some paint fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and minor staining, but all essential electronics and controls are in working order. Mechanically, it remains reliable for everyday commutes, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. It is a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility and value over aesthetics.",
