    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that sits at the pinnacle of its class. This car has been maintained to a standard rarely seen on the secondary market, offering a factory-fresh experience for the next owner. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it has been treated with a ceramic coating to preserve its luster. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, retaining that new-car aroma with premium leather surfaces that show zero signs of wear or bolster compression. Every technological feature and driver-assist system operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete service history performed exclusively by authorized specialists. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle in flawless, turn-key condition.",
