      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car is in stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one, always kept it garage-tucked, and it still has that fresh feel inside and out! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
