      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-locked limited-slip differential, this vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis is free of subframe fatigue, and the suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings for peak lateral grip. Finished in a flawless coat with zero orange peel, this high-revving naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. A true turnkey collector piece for the discerning purist.",
